                                                                 java.lang.String queryID,
                                                                 java.lang.String serverAddress,
                                                                 java.util.List<java.lang.String> tsdbImportList)
        Generate a list of ImportRecords containing one ImportRecord per tsdb implementation on given server for a given time series.
        Parameters:
        timeSeriesList - the time series to be imported.
        queryID - the query id
        serverAddress - the server address or ip on which the import should be done.
        tsdbImportList - a list of tsdb names on which the import should be done. null == all available on server
        Returns:
        list of ImportRecords.

        Generate a list of QueryRecords containing one QueryRecord per tsdb implementation on given server for given times seres meta data.
        Parameters:
        timeSeriesMetaDataList - the time series meta data which should be queried.
        queryID - the query id
        serverAddress - the server address or ip on which the queries should be done.
        function - the query function which should be performed.
        p - the percentile value (if needed, null if not).
